Harlen O. MORGAN, Petitioner, v. UNITED STATES FEDERAL PAROLE BOARD, UNITED STATES PENITENTIARY, AtLANTA, GEORGIA, Respondent. No. 7399. Circuit Court of Appeals, Fifth Circuit. July 6, 1934.

Before BRYAN, FOSTER, and SIBLEY, Circuit Judges.

PER CURIAM.

The petition for mandamus in the above numbered and entitled cause is denied.
